# DESIGN Domain — Visual Identity & Design System

DESIGN_RULE_0=Theme: dark-first. Background #000 (--background). Text #fff (--foreground). Accent #FF10F0 (--color-accent).
DESIGN_RULE_1=Accent hover: #e00dd6 (--color-accent-hover). Use CSS vars, not hardcoded hex in components.
DESIGN_RULE_2=Typography: Inter font. Headings clamp() responsive — h1: clamp(3rem,10vw,8rem), h2: clamp(2rem,6vw,5rem), h3: clamp(1.5rem,4vw,3rem).
DESIGN_RULE_3=Headings: font-weight 700, line-height 1.1, letter-spacing -0.02em. Body text: opacity 0.8 by default.
DESIGN_RULE_4=Section padding: clamp(4rem,8vw,8rem). Content max-width: 1400px with mx-auto.
DESIGN_RULE_5=Accent glow pattern: radial-gradient with accent at ~8% opacity for background ambiance. Common across sections.
DESIGN_RULE_6=Cards/containers: bg-white/5 (subtle glass), border border-white/10, rounded-2xl or rounded-3xl, backdrop-blur optional.
DESIGN_RULE_7=Buttons: accent bg with black text, rounded-full, font-bold. Hover scale(1.05). Secondary: border-white/20 transparent bg.
DESIGN_RULE_8=Transitions: fast 150ms, base 300ms cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1), slow 500ms. Use CSS vars --transition-*.
DESIGN_RULE_9=Selection color: accent bg with black text. Scrollbar: accent thumb on black track, 8px width.
